### OAuth Get Token
# @name getToken
POST https://oauth.example.com/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials&client_id=my-client&client_secret=my-secret

### Use OAuth Token from previous request
# @name useToken
GET https://api.example.com/secured
Authorization: Bearer {{getToken.response.body.access_token}}
